highlights.text: Anson Lo 盧瀚霆 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “Lemonade” is the highest at #3.
“12 to 12” by sombr is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hong Kong at #190.
“反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1565 days straight.
“特別的人” by Khalil Fong is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 51 spots at #120.
